</li><li><strong>Ich hätte gerne eine neue Stelle. </strong>I would like to have a new job.
</li><li><strong>gut / schlecht verdienen </strong>to earn well / poorly
</li><li><strong>stressig </strong>stressful
</li><li><strong>arbeitslos sein </strong>unemployed
